igure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"left\",\"id\":110,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft size-large\"><img src=\"http://18.191.201.89/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Secondary-1-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-110\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Marca','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2020-04-23 16:26:08','2020-04-23 19:26:08','','42','http://18.191.201.89/wordpress/index.php/2020/04/23/42-revision-v1/','0','revision','','0'), ('112','1','2020-04-23 16:27:24','2020-04-23 19:27:24','','Headers','','inherit','open','closed','','headers','','','2020-04-23 16:27:24','2020-04-23 19:27:24','','49','http://18.191.201.89/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Headers.png','0','attachment','image/png','0'), ('113','1','2020-04-23 16:27:36','2020-04-23 19:27:36','','Body','','inherit','open','closed','','body','','','2020-04-23 16:27:36','2020-04-23 19:27:36','','49','http://18.191.201.89/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Body.png','0','attachment','image/png','0'), ('114','1','2020-04-23 16:27:48','2020-04-23 19:27:48','','Placeholder','','inherit','open','closed','','placeholder','','','2020-04-23 16:27:48','2020-04-23 19:27:48','','49','http://18.191.201.89/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Placeholder.png','0','attachment','image/png','0'), ('115','1','2020-04-23 16:27:51','2020-04-23 19:27:51','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Seguindo os padrões do <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/UNDERSTANDING-WCAG20/visual-audio-contrast-contrast.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">W3C</a>, o texto e os elementos de segundo plano devem atingir o contraste mínimo de <strong>4,5: 1</strong> ( nível AA) para fontes iguais ou menores que 14 pt, exceto:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Textos grandes (18,6px ou 14px em negrito) devem manter o contraste de pelo menos 3: 1 ( nível A